_header: Thou Achilles in battle me slew
_description: A Mumming of the Nine Worthies — nine couplets

BodTan407.First Lines:
Thow achylles in bataly me slowOf my wurthynes men speken I
                    now…
BodTan407.Last Lines:
…And I was kyng of IherusalemThe crowne of thorn I wan fro
                    hem
